SELECT sr.id, sr.dateCreated, sr.C_serReqDmccSrNo, c.c_licenseNumber, sr.c_serReqServCat, 
c.c_companyName, c.c_companyLocation, t.c_tower_seq_no, t.c_tower_name ,sr.c_status 
FROM app_fd_ofc_serreqs_tab sr
INNER JOIN app_fd_ofc_company_tab c
ON sr.c_companyName = c.id
INNER JOIN app_fd_ofc_location_tab l
ON c.c_companyLocation = l.c_locName
INNER JOIN app_fd_ofc_tower_tab t
ON c.c_tower_name = t.c_tower_name
WHERE sr.c_status = 'Payment Completed' or sr.c_status = 'Inspection Scheduled'
